source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_SEQ_00<tab>Tonaxia is beside herself in giggling glee.
target: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_SEQ_00<tab>Tonaxia réfléchit visiblement à sa prochaine farce.

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_SEQ_01<tab>Despite her attempts to play innocent, it is evident that Tonaxia is in need of ingredients for her latest prank. Strike out for Larkscall; slay a morbol, an old-growth treant, and two molted ziz; and harvest the malodorous items she seeks─a phial of morbol bile, a rotting acorn, and two phials of ziz venom, respectively.
target: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_SEQ_01<tab>Tonaxia vous a demandé de lui rapporter <var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E88DE0202 /var>, <var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E88DF0202 /var> et deux <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E88E00302 /var>. Vous pouvez les obtenir en tuant les morbols, les tréants centenaires et les ziz déplumés qui vivent à Chantalouette.

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_SEQ_02<tab>The unpleasant creatures are no more, and their unpleasant remains are yours. Deliver the aforementioned goods to Tonaxia.
target: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez obtenu les objets dont Tonaxia a besoin. Portez-les-lui au Refuge avant que leur odeur n'imprègne vos vêtements.

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_SEQ_03<tab>Tonaxia is pleased to receive the items she requested, and promises that you will not be the victim of her foul-smelling plot─provided, of course, you continue to do her bidding.
target: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_SEQ_03<tab>Vous avez remis avec soulagement les produits pestilentiels demandés par Tonaxia. La victime de son prochain canular est pro<var 16 /var>ba<var 16 /var>ble<var 16 /var>ment à plaindre...

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TODO_00<tab>Defeat a morbol to obtain a phial of morbol bile.
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TODO_01<tab>Defeat an old-growth treant to obtain a rotting acorn.
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TODO_02<tab>Defeat molted ziz to obtain phials of ziz venom.
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TODO_03<tab>Deliver the requested goods to Tonaxia.
target: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TODO_03<tab>Donner les produits pestilentiels à Tonaxia

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_000<tab>This might be this one's most ingenious trick ever! This one cannot wait to see walking one's face when this one─oh?
target:
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_000<tab>Hi hi hi, j'ai trouvé la farce idéale,
ce sera un véritable régal<var 1D /var>!
Pour rire, quoi de mieux qu'une exquise puanteur,
quoi de plus drôle qu'une abjecte odeur<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_001<tab>Trick? This one said nothing of the sort. This one thinks walking one's ears are the ones playing tricks.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_001<tab>T-tu m'as entendu<var 1D /var>!? Bon, c'est promis, je ne te ferai rien,
mais seulement si tu me donnes un coup de main.

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_002<tab>But perhaps walking one could help this one gather some valuable ingredients...since walking one seems to have free hands.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_002<tab>Il y a des monstres dans les environs,
dont les parties du corps sont une vraie infection.

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_003<tab>This one requires one phial of morbol bile, one rotten treant acorn, and two phials of ziz venom─the stinkier, the better! Why, walking one asks? That is...ah, a secret.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_003<tab><var 2B ((<var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E88DE0202 /var>)) /var> pour commencer,
<var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E88DF0202 /var> pour continuer.
Des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF0ED0302 /var> tu obtiens le premier,
et des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF0E90302 /var>, le deuxième objet.

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_004<tab>Larkscall is full of stinky ones. Walking one will find everything this one needs there.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_004<tab>En tuant deux <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF0DE0302 /var> pour finir,
tu auras des <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E88E00302 /var>, ça devrait suffire.

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_010<tab>This one requires one phial of morbol bile, one rotten treant acorn, and two phials of ziz venom─the stinkier, the better! Why? Did this one not say it was a secret?
target:
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_010<tab><var 2B ((<var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E88DE0202 /var>)) /var> pour commencer,
<var 33 ((EventItem)) 02F61E88DF0202 /var> pour continuer.
Des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF0ED0302 /var> tu obtiens le premier,
et des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF0E90302 /var>, le deuxième objet.

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_011<tab>Larkscall is full of stinky ones. Walking one will find everything this one needs there.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_011<tab>En tuant deux <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF0DE0302 /var> pour finir,
tu auras des <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E88E00302 /var>, ça devrait suffire.

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_020<tab>Well, did walking one find what this one needs from stinky ones?
target:
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_020<tab>Me rapportes-tu ce que je t'ai demandé<var 1D /var>?
Certainement, ce n'est pas trop compliqué<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_030<tab>Perfect! Yes, this will be the stinkiest trick ever! Tee hee hee!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_030<tab>Oh, c'est ce qu'il me faut exactement<var 1D /var>!
Je vais pouvoir jouer quelques tours amusants<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_031<tab>Do not worry, walking one, this one will not play it on walking one. As long as walking one keeps doing what this one says. Tee hee!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL102_01258_TONAXIA_000_031<tab>Tu fais un<var 08 E905 ((e excellente)) (( excellent)) /var> complice,
nous sommes unis par une même malice<var 1D /var>!
